# ESP32 Custom Partition Table Example (4MB flash with OTA support)
# Name,    Type, SubType,  Offset,   Size,     Flags
#
# Total size must fit within flash_size from project.json
# This example: 4MB = 0x400000
#
# Layout:
#   - NVS for WiFi creds, settings
#   - OTA data for tracking active app slot
#   - 2 app partitions (~1.3 MB each) for OTA
#   - SPIFFS for file storage (~1.4 MB)
#   - Coredump for crash diagnostics (64 KB)
#
nvs,       data, nvs,      0x9000,   0x5000,
otadata,   data, ota,      0xe000,   0x2000,
app0,      app,  ota_0,    0x10000,  0x140000,
app1,      app,  ota_1,    0x150000, 0x140000,
spiffs,    data, spiffs,   0x290000, 0x160000,
coredump,  data, coredump, 0x3F0000, 0x10000,
